{
  "stem": "6526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And us especially, we did not have any problem because we had a business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And mostly the precinct, there were four or five policemen-- four-- probably four.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And mostly, they were stationed almost in our house because they looked to get-- to get paid and they always looked for how to get paid is from truck men that the light didn't was on, or there's this.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the pay was a half a pack of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The half a pack of cigarettes-- there were 10 cigarettes-- was $0.50, 50 Russian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big deal to them, but during the night they could make quite a few-- quite a few zlotys.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you have any-- do you have any memory of incidents in the relationship between you and some of the Polish kids?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We occasionally used to fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to call us cebula, which means onion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we used to call them kapusta, which is--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--cabbage.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But especially those-- that was a fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But no-- no special fight, no ordinary fights like hitting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There might have been somebody hit, but not in the form that you can here-- see it here on televisions, or hear what's going on in places that people attack other ones just because he thinks the other one has money.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not exactly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they-- they-- it-- it was-- it originated much before me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we knew that we call them kapusta, and they used to call us cebula.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because first of all, the Jews like onions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And maybe they like kapusta.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe they liked cabbage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, we had cabbage also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But maybe different tasting and things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish communal life before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember there was a Kehillah made out of Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
